name: MO
description: This series of collages in one way or another touches on the topic of time, understanding, perception of time. This is because I took as a basis old photographs of artists who are similar to me and even fit in age (in the photographs), but now, besides the photographs, there is a big difference. It is very interesting to watch how it turned out unpredictable the fate of the artists who at that time were like us and were considered modern and progressive.
